location.fullValue: Julian Plan, The Springs at Skyline Trails

data.description: Welcome to this charming three bedroom, two bathroom home with true study that exudes warmth and character at every turn. As you approach the front entrance, you'll be captivated by the enticing curb appeal, featuring a welcoming porch perfect for enjoying your morning coffee. As you step inside you'll be greeted by the open concept design of the home that creates a spacious and airy atmosphere, making it ideal for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen is remarkable with quartz countertops, a gas range and a farmhouse sink in the oversized island. Step into the expansive master bedroom that seamlessly connects to the ensuite bathroom, featuring a sizable vanity, walk-in shower and a spacious closet. Adding to the home's charm, you'll find two more bedrooms, each with its own individual appeal, and a dedicated true study, which collectively come together to form the perfect embodiment of this inviting home. The backyard has plenty of room to run and entertain. Neighborhood features a playground and splashpad. Welcome Home!
